uientry.unicode: Some defences can only be used during the development stage.
Remove mine||Click this to remove any mines you have placed if you want to reposition them.
Place mine (must be outside the enemy deployment zone)||Mines make excellent traps, but be careful of sailing your own ships into them by mistake.
Deploy screens||These defences block projectiles and create obstructions to enemy movement.
Deploy bamboo wall||These defences create obstructions to enemy movement.
